		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://handown.wordpress.com/2013/11/19/bitcoin/" rel="bookmark">Bitcoin</a></h2>		<p>I am now part of the <a title="Bitcoin" href="http://bitcoin.org/en/" target="_blank">Bitcoin</a> network.  I have a computer at home which is powered and connected to the internet 24/7 and it is running the <a title="Full-Node software" href="http://bitcoin.org/en/download" target="_blank">full-node software</a> to help make the Bitcoin network more stable and accessible.</p>
<p>I would appreciate any donations of bitcoin you can spare so that I can continue running this computer and also get some bitcoins to use in this exciting economy.  My wallet address is: <span style="color:#ff6600;"><strong>1MwGNsenPT413GtqptTJ5t75JuHshRL8VP</strong></span></p>

	<div class="clear"></div>
