		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://handown.wordpress.com/2012/11/18/new-eden-open/" rel="bookmark">New Eden Open</a></h2>		<p>I am seeing <a href="http://www.own3d.tv/CCPGames/live/307014" target="_blank">New Eden Open</a> tournament.  I really wish to participate in such events but my circle of EVE friends is not connected to the people that participate, and as always in EVE, solo gets you nowhere.  It is a sad and sometimes frustrating feeling.</p>

